replies.body: Caitlyn headshot? Did you know that she used to be able to crit for about 3000 HP back in patch 5.22? Those were the good ol days when Caitlyn was hidden OP. Saw a Vayne rush from their fountain only to be one shot by a Caitlyn (when Shiv+RFC used to stack damage). So funny!
it was probs cait on a minion or camp
What it is, is higher than many champions max Hp.....
